            "text": "<p>Our European production guarantees the highest quality standards and allows us to monitor and control every step of the manufacturing process. </p><p>From selecting high-quality raw materials to the careful bottling of each fragrance, we ensure that every product meets our strict requirements for quality and craftsmanship.</p>",
